data.description: Welcome to your updated move in ready home in highly sought after Mainstreet neighborhood!! Spacious great room open to the eat in kitchen with breakfast bar, updated cabinets, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, pantry and stainless-steel appliances. Primary ensuite with his & her closets, garden tub, newer vanity with quartz countertop. Newer vinyl plank flooring in all living spaces, lighting, hardware, roof and the list goes on! French doors leading to fenced in backyard with oversized patio and firepit. Walking distance to schools, shopping, convenient to 1-95 - approx. 35 minutes to Fort Stewart, 30 minutes to Hyundai Plant, 20 minutes to Gulfstream. Amenity filled neighborhood offering community pool, lake, trails, and playground. This is the one you don't want to miss, call your favorite Realtor today!
